pokedexEntries.gold: It makes a nest to suit its long and skinny body. The nest is impossible for other Pokémon to enter.
pokedexEntries.silver: There is no telling where the tail begins. Despite its short legs, it is quick at hunting Rattata.
pokedexEntries.crystal: It lives in narrow burrows that fit its slim body. The deeper the nests go, the more maze-like they become.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Furret has a very slim build. When under attack, it can slickly squirm through narrow spaces and get away. In spite of its short limbs, this Pokémon is very nimble and fleet.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Furret has a very slim build. When under attack, it can slickly squirm through narrow spaces and get away. In spite of its short limbs, this Pokémon is very nimble and fleet.
